{"tid":102962,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"訂機票名打少左個字母","createTime":"2017-02-01T03:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T07:56:26.000Z","uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"159c622e96e3743737ccd761fb6eeeaa4ee9408c","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"想問下巴絲有冇試過係平機票網訂機票<br />\n但打少左個名 英文拼音一個字母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例：<br />\n正確為：CHEUNG WAN YAN<br />\n打少左：CHEUNG WAN YA<br />\n我係GOGOGO TRAVEL到訂長榮航空既機票<br />\n已知GOGOGO TRAVEL 改名要收$350<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打去問長榮想知佢地果邊要收多幾多手續費<br />\n話答唔到我... 佢地要睇Agent...<br />\n<br />\n有冇機會我直接當日係長榮地勤櫃位改唔洗錢<br />\n或者唔洗比咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次第一次幫人買就搞啲咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e48c7853bc88968163ec497cd355af3c0879dc","tid":102962,"uid":48012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"Walkin搞 有機會係個名太長佢個電腦食少左隻字 未必係你打漏"},{"pid":"57e09180a2f32f18c8780caeb2f165f81faea748","tid":102962,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"直接打電話去航空公司"},{"pid":"c225172c5f8c32be0e374e1cb53b7effb8918d82","tid":102962,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"呢個情況好難唔收手續費。"},{"pid":"fbc26ccd481b007ec0becbfb4f304b51f6ad8574","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Walkin搞 有機會係個名太長佢個電腦食少左隻字 未必係你打漏</blockquote><br />\n...應該唔係<br />\n同行有個friend個名再長啲...<br />\n係我自己衰打漏左..."},{"pid":"9794f054faa45779320470e2132c17294dfbda72","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接打電話去航空公司</blockquote><br />\n打左...佢地話要睇agent...<br />\n唔知咩意思.."},{"pid":"c832dc8543a73445c291250aa0a5fb99dc11cf1e","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e2c70503973f85b759df8272c9e6b65e4f9cfa","tid":102962,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"夠膽咪唔好搞<br />\n自己打少隻字仲咁多野講<br />\n人地有權唔比你改 <br />\n三百幾蚊仲想點"},{"pid":"a292db75c9b0523df82c49db143480363827534b","tid":102962,"uid":3739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總之你要改就要收架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想比咪唔好改囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4f5030e99ceec465a98c8d5b1a9ac7c8138c70","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠膽咪唔好搞<br />\n自己打少隻字仲咁多野講<br />\n人地有權唔比你改 <br />\n三百幾蚊仲想點</blockquote><br />\n都係既...唔洗重新買過已經好好.."},{"pid":"fe45ad0a826ada756c14a506ebf5d3eb05881dc0","tid":102962,"uid":47888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"睇你幾時發現<br />\n<br />\n情況一：<br />\n出發前3個月，我係達哥神鵰到買套票，俾左錢發現錯名即刻打去客服，佢話航空公司未出票可以幫我成張cancel再買<br />\n<br />\n情況二：<br />\n同事買左快運機票，幾日先知打錯，打去改350蚊一粒字<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住錯名去地勤到免費改（佢地至撚憎呢類人）一黎冇得改，二黎唔會俾你上機，最壞程況係要買過張機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多師奶試過唔俾佢上機係到又投訴又剩，問候地勤全家，犯眾憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿拿聲350蚊俾左佢，確保旅程愈快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907b6d4ace03768ec0b529c75885c5ee830fab10","tid":102962,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為資料既野錯就係錯"},{"pid":"70eceb4363d6d03f655fd9dff9a7497907abaee0","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你幾時發現<br />\n<br />\n情況一：<br />\n出發前3個月，我係達哥神鵰到買套票，俾左錢發現錯名即刻打去客服，佢話航空公司未出票可以幫我成張cancel再買<br />\n<br />\n情況二：<br />\n同事買左快運機票，幾日先知打錯，打去改350蚊一粒字<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住錯名去地勤到免費改（佢地至撚憎呢類人）一黎冇得改，二黎唔會俾你上機，最壞程況係要買過張機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多師奶試過唔俾佢上機係到又投訴又剩，問候地勤全家，犯眾憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿拿聲350蚊俾左佢，確保旅程愈快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明白！謝謝你"},{"pid":"7dfd0fcd1e5b0c6475684411eb05bf32c0763d07","tid":102962,"uid":40599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為資料既野錯就係錯</blockquote><br />\n明白 下次要小心啲"},{"pid":"7f054e2a8c0bc85921bf70ffcbd42c5f5d7d56e7","tid":102962,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"比錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n確定買之前俾你Double check一次又唔睇清楚<br />\n唔啱資料分分鐘上唔到機"},{"pid":"b86c10f8f89fda5bc409b4553dc3cbc635903d10","tid":102962,"uid":29513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"唔岩資料連機都冇得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9daffae86c16e4024007c0c0e77dcae1d4f0f578","tid":102962,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"去入境處改名做CHEUNG WAN YA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97227380ccb48c3cc9a32fa10040aaf79784ad2e","tid":102962,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得出呢句都知樓主有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6a45e11902759847e2253e82139f7f63f56e5b","tid":102962,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個情況好難唔收手續費。</blockquote><br />\n其實少左一個字母 仲要唔係個姓錯<br />\n唔明點解要罰咁多... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打錯名通常得兩個情況，一係比手續費改名，一係錯得過份既分分鐘連機都上唔到。"},{"pid":"51407e765bfcc9916e286662293c25796d712e89","tid":102962,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"試過臨上機發現m打左n<br />\n改字收500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef02b130700bfb1a48ffb1a5000c733bef5283f5","tid":102962,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 自己做錯野<br />\n幾百蚊都想省 仆你個街啦食屎狗"},{"pid":"88dadf77a5045c2984437a416e4c0a019cdc29c1","tid":102962,"uid":4070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":